Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you're Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to know the name of\Nthe criminal who's going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He risked his life for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma,\Nwhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to where\NInspector Lunge is, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, too. I have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter that Inspector Lunge\Ngave to Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Inspector Lunge\Nfound it at Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've been watching you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've been watching\Nso I could devour you whole."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"But instead,\Neverything about you consumed me."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"When I was falling apart,\Nhow did I look to you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"When I was falling apart,\Nthe object that you gave me.. ."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"You left me a beautiful jewel."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"The twins who look as if they\Nwere blessed with eternal life."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"The most sinful deed is to\Ntake away a person's name."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's get your name back."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll give you your name back."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your name is Anna."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right now, I'm just sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I. ..fell in love with\Nthe mother of the twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind changed in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who knew about her. ..\Nabout the twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and about the experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get that wound treated,\Nit'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me if you\Nwant to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you go\Nso far for Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your relationship\Nwith him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen quite far in the world,\Nhaven't you, Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA's best investigator is in\Nthis rural village all by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You went sightseeing\Nwithout a badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You investigated too deep into a\Nscandal involving a parliament member
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and lost work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chasing Tenma became\Nyour only reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm impressed\Nyou researched that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife.. .\NIs living with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And your grandson thinks\Nthat man is his grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He can speak now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And he calls him\N"Grandpa, Grandpa."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see him,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandson is\Ngrowing up beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see him,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The old Inspector Lunge\Nwasn't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who am I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's my relationship\Nwith Johan?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no name. I have no country.\NI have no memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, I was out\Nof the orphanage and working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One day,\NJohan appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He awakened\None of my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His own name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he was\Nfrom an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he had\Nforgotten everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but he remembered\Nhis friend's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He forgot his name,\Nbut remembered his friend's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. His friend liked\Ndrawing and bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't like killing bugs,\Nso he let them go from their cages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe his name was...\NAdolph Reinhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved the hot cocoa that was\Ngiven to them once each week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan came to me. ..\Nand handed me a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered the thing I looked\Nforward to each week in that orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved that hot cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if the rain\Nwould wash everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear, hate, and sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even on that day,\Nit was raining like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Liebert, former head of\Nthe East German Trade Commission,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who fled to the West from\NEast Germany just the other day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}appeared before the media\Nwith his wife and children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Lieberts didn't appear\Nto be exhausted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And their two children have\Nbright expressions on their faces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a refugee as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. From Czechoslovakia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that you\Nknow the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just their\Nsleeping faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A tragedy occurred\Nthat night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One girl is confirmed\Nto be alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A man and a woman\Nare dead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boy is in serious condition\Nbut he has a pulse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's the patient?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blood pressure, 72/50...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pulse, 138!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bullet went in\Nthrough his forehead?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what in the world\Nhad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew everything,\Nbut I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped thinking about\Nanything and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pictures of those ideal twins...\NOf them surrounded by love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But. ..no matter how many I drew,\NI couldn't draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I knew that\Nit didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge is at Hotel Bergbach.\NThat's just up ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know where\Nthey're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I created a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought that monster\Nback to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't kill you, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much grip\Nin my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma shot me\Nin a library in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been easy\Nto kill him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is the one\Nwho's to be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be the one left in the end. ..\Nall alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to die\Nalone and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of Johan's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma will be allowed to\Nsee the sight Johan has seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see that sight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge...\Nyou won't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also part of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer in my head tells me\Nthat doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's watching this\Nfrom somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he were watching\Na line of ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's look inside.\NTenma was headed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Is anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. We're on your side.\NWe've come to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. I'm not holding anything.\NOkay? It's all right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman in the picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"The woman in the picture"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You look exactly like the girl\Nin those pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Lots of pictures"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a boy with the same face.\NThey were pictures of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you\Nsee those pictures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you see them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The hill to the south...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At the "Vampire's House."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Does anybody know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where my son is?\NHey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim, where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil has come\Nto this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan was here just\Na moment ago doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all attempts at\Ndrawing the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But they were left unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pictures look like\Nthey're smiling affectionately...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But did Franz Bonaparta\Ndraw these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Johan do upon\Nseeing these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back. Welcome home.
